+config IMA_RTMR
+	bool "Extend IMA measurements to CC runtime measurement registers"
+	depends on IMA && KRETPROBES && TSM_MEASUREMENTS
+	help
+	  Extends IMA measurements to Confidential Computing runtime
+	  measurement registers (e.g. TDX RTMR) via the tsm-mr sysfs
+	  interface. The module hooks ima_add_template_entry() using a
+	  kretprobe and writes template digests to the target register.
+
+	  If unsure, say N.
+
